[normal]1.
[normal]              
[normal]The 
[normal]House of Commons Science and Technology Committee (hereinafter the S &amp; T C
[normal]ommittee
[normal])
[normal] has announced its intention to hold an enquiry into what the public understand about climate, where people look for their information, and how that may impact on climate change policy
[normal]; and it has invited written submissions. Such is the nature of the present document.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]2.
[normal]              
[normal]The invitation requires that each submission 
[normal]should 
[normal]include a declaration of interest
[normal].
